n playing style and some roleplay more than others.  To debunk someone because they'd use an item you personally wouldn't and rip their playing, etc, shows you really have to learn more about EQ, it's not about the mobs, it's about the people you meet.  Quite honestly, keep ripping others like you did on the boards just because some sk may use this weapon, you're gonna find yourself in more ignore lists and less groups.  Just a small possiblity of why your rating is bumping the lower realms of 'aweful.'<br><br>Good luck in the hunt, be safe.  May your aim be true, your blade sharp, and your dodge be fast.<br>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=546090 target=_new>Baraka Lonesoul</a><br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=546804 target=_new>Decimusx</a><br>Brell Serilis</td></tr>
